---
const title = "Nightstage Hello World";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg-start: #0f172a;
        --bg-end: #1d4ed8;
        --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        --text: #eff6ff;
        --accent: #fbbf24;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2), transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-start), var(--bg-end));
        color: var(--text);
      }

      main {
        width: min(90vw, 720px);
        padding: 3rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: var(--card);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.35);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 4.75rem);
        line-height: 0.95;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 34rem;
      }

      strong {
        color: var(--accent);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Hello World</h1>
      <p>
        Este proyecto en <strong>Astro</strong> ya esta listo para arrancar, probar y
        publicar en GitHub con la cuenta de Nightstage.
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
